com.brashmonkey.spriter

Class Timeline.Key.Bone

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brashmonkey.spriter.Timeline.Key.Bone
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Player.Attachment, Timeline.Key.Object
    Enclosing class:
    Timeline.Key

    public static class Timeline.Key.Bone
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a bone in a Spriter SCML file. A bone holds a position, scale, an angle and a pivot. Bones are the only objects which can be used as a parent for other tweenable objects.
